OL,7,FAfter months of research I was about
OL,8,Fto interview my first victim of
OL,9,Fspiking, but Nikki Garnett's story
OL,10,Fwasn't one I was expecting.
OL,12,FThe 57 year old was out having a few
OL,13,Fdrinks with her husband in Newcastle
OL,14,Fwhen she suddenly felt very
OL,15,F"different".
OL,17,F"I literally took one foot off the
OL,18,Fpavement. It was so quick to cross the
OL,19,Froad... and I felt like I was just
OL,20,Fgoing down,"
