OL,7,F"My husband looked around a bit
OL,8,Fsurprised and said, are you okay?
OL,9,FBecause we hadn't had that much to
OL,10,Fdrink, you know, thinking what on
OL,11,Fearth's going on?
OL,13,F"And I tried to say no, I'm not okay.
OL,14,FAs I was trying to verbalize it,
OL,15,Fabsolute nonsense was coming out of my
OL,16,Fmouth, absolute gibberish. I couldn't
OL,17,Fspeak."
