OL,7,FSpiking is the act of putting a
OL,8,Fsubstance into someone's drink, or
OL,9,Finto their body through another
OL,10,Fmethod, without their consent. It can
OL,11,Fhappen to anyone at any time, but it
OL,12,Fdisproportionally affects women.
OL,14,FWhile trying to understand the true
OL,15,Fscale of spiking across the UK, we
OL,16,Frealised the problem is that you
OL,17,Fsimply can't know the full extent.
OL,19,FIt's an underreported crime. Some
OL,20,Fpeople I spoke to didn't even know it
OL,21,Fwas illegal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/23
