OL,7,FCampaigners say the reason is that
OL,8,Fit's been trivialised for too long.
OL,10,FFor example, in films like 'The
OL,11,FHangover', where the plot centres
OL,12,Faround spiking, or 'ironic' jokes like
OL,13,Fthe one made by the former Home
OL,14,FSecretary James Cleverley, suggesting
OL,15,Fhe put Rohypnol in his wife's drink `
OL,16,Ffor which he's since apologised.
OL,18,FCampaigners say they believe it's
OL,19,Foften not deemed that important or
OL,20,Fserious.
