OL,7,FUnlike other types of assault, there's
OL,8,Fa short time limit on proving spiking.
OL,10,FDrugs often only last in the body for
OL,11,Fup to about 12 hours, or in some cases
OL,12,Feven less time, so unless a victim has
OL,13,Fa police approved drugs testing kit on
OL,14,Fthem and has the capacity to test
OL,15,Fthemselves or be tested quickly ,
OL,16,Fthere will often be no hard evidence
OL,17,Fthe spiking took place, other than the
OL,18,Fvictim's word.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/23
