OL,7,FNot only do police have to prove who
OL,8,Fadministered the narcotics and that
OL,9,Fthey were given without consent, they
OL,10,Fhave to prove that drugs were in the
OL,11,Fvictims system in the first place, and
OL,12,Fthat requires police forensics, not
OL,13,FNHS medical tests.
OL,15,FSo many people I spoke to told me they
OL,16,Fdidn't bother telling the police
OL,17,Fbecause they thought they wouldn't be
OL,18,Fbelieved.
