OL,7,FColin and Mandy's son died while he
OL,8,Fwas in his college halls of residence.
OL,9,FThey believe he was spiked
OL,11,F"We need a standalone offence. We need
OL,12,Fit to be clear. No confusion, not
OL,13,Fmocked up and tied in with other
OL,14,Foffences. Just a straight - if you are
OL,15,Fspiked, the police will treat the
OL,16,Fmatter the same way. And that's what
OL,17,Fwe want," Colin said.
