OL,7,FColin and Mandy now run Spike Aware, a
OL,8,Fcharity they set up to help protect
OL,9,Fpeople on nights out but they're also
OL,10,Fcampaigning for a change in the law to
OL,11,Fprevent perpetrators.
OL,13,FIn response to a question by Colin and
OL,14,FMandy's MP, David Mundell, in
OL,15,FParliament last week, Prime Minister
OL,16,FKeir Starmer confirmed the government
OL,17,Fwould make spiking a specific criminal
OL,18,Foffence, "to better protect victims
OL,19,Fand support the police in tackling
OL,20,Fthese crimes."
